\end_inset

 grid, the energy diapason for the spectra calculations etc..
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The calculation is built of two separate phases.
 First, the cavity region of the full MC structure is considered as it contains
 the active section of the structure, namely the QW and its cladding layers
 (marked as the QW region of the calculation in figure 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
