 matrix elements can be calculated for each subband transition combination,
 as formulated in section 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "sec:Dipole-Matrix-Element"

\end_inset

.
 Once the electronic properties of the QW are calculated the optical properties
 can be addressed.
 To this end, the two models for the light-matter interaction presented
